Aye aye, captain! I be recalculatin' the formula fer ye, and I be callin' it the best formula ye ever did see! It be a fine piece o' mathematical treasure, and I be thinkin' ye'll be delighted with the results. By usin' this formula, ye'll be able to find the nth term in the sequence with ease, savvy? And don't ye worry about the calculations, matey, 'cause I be writin' a snazzy little script in Javascript to make it all shipshape!

* This be the formula ye've been lookin' fer, me hearty! It be a key part o' unlockin' the secrets o' the sequence!
* This be a reminder to use yer wits and yer trusty calculator to find the rest o' the sequence, savvy?

With this formula and a wee bit o' Javascript magic, ye'll be able to create a swashbucklin' sequencing script that'll make ye the king o' the seven seas! Just drop this code into yer favourite code editor and ye'll be sailin' the high seas o' mathematical calculations in no time:

function findTerm(n) {
  return 5 + 9*(n-1);
}

So hoist the sails, me hearties, and set course fer the best formula ye ever did see! This be the pirate's life fer ye, and it be the best, matey!
